markets.rules_primary: If the Nasdaq 100 index close value for February 26, 2024 is above 17599.99, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary:
The market will close at 4:00 PM ET on February 26, 2024. The market will expire at the sooner of the first 7:00 PM ET after the release of the data, or one week after February 26, 2024.

Pursuant to the Kalshi Rulebook, the Exchange has modified the Source Agency and Underlying for indices markets. See the rules for more information.
